  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "(1) The Empire, my adversary.\n\n(2) The revolutionary secret Christians, my colleagues.\n\nThis is my Dasein, k my way of being, in the phylogonic world. How could I ever have failed to see that the world revealed to me by anamnesis is the same as the world of the phylogons, reticulated and arborizing, with the new accretions con¬ stantly being laid down. Of course: in that phylogonic world the revolutionary secret Christian underground Is always attacking the Prison; these are precisely phylogons ",
      "matched_alias": "Dasein",
      "term_id": "TERM_dasein",
      "term_name": "Dasein",
      "term_slug": "dasein"
    },
    {
      "text": "I have been thinking for several hours about this realm of the phylogons which apparently I was in by what I have long called anamnesis. This is an introduction into immortality, but I think there is only one way you can be introduced into that world. It as a world is the world gesta Christi, and it must be the Holy Spirit who awakens your perception to that world. It is not the afterlife and it is not reincarnation; it is a world of eternal constants, and these constants point to Christianity w",
      "matched_alias": "Form World",
      "term_id": "TERM_form-world",
      "term_name": "Form World",
      "term_slug": "form-world"
    },
    {
      "text": "-24-\n\nthe strong (Yang) and enantiodromia of estrangement of the opposites, total bipolarization, into reconciliation, the hierogamy. This would be quite some transformation: weak into strong (Yin into Yang, or Form Two into Form One) and total estrangement into total reconcilia¬ tion and equilibrium (this would also be Empedocles' strife turning into love thus producing a total krasis in me). (And based on the micro- macrocosmic principle of correspondence, like to like, I would then perceive t",
      "matched_alias": "Western",
      "term_id": "TERM_western",
      "term_name": "Western",
      "term_slug": "western"
    }
  ],
